00:20:17,770 --> 00:20:21,149
Begitu mereka yang kabur
dengan 300 juta dolar itu tertangkap,

222
00:20:21,232 --> 00:20:23,902
kita akan bisa hidup mewah
seperti dahulu.

223
00:20:23,985 --> 00:20:25,111
Sayang, dengar.

224
00:20:25,195 --> 00:20:26,654
Ini peluang yang ditakdirkan.

225
00:20:26,738 --> 00:20:28,907
Kau harus menyelesaikannya.

226
00:20:28,990 --> 00:20:30,033
Charlotte.

227
00:20:30,116 --> 00:20:31,075
Ya?

228
00:20:31,993 --> 00:20:33,286
Berikan Ray-Ban milikku.

229
00:20:41,211 --> 00:20:44,297
Hei, buka pintunya! Sekarang!

230
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,798
Buka!

231
00:20:45,882 --> 00:20:47,342
-Buka!
-Berengsek!

232
00:20:47,425 --> 00:20:49,844
-Buka pintunya sekarang!
-Han-na.

233
00:20:49,928 --> 00:20:51,804
-Han-na?
-Ya, Pak.

234
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:55,850
STUDIO REKAMAN 1

235
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,693
Sial.

236
00:21:07,028 --> 00:21:08,071
Han-na.

237
00:21:08,821 --> 00:21:09,864
Kau membuatku takut.

238
00:21:32,053 --> 00:21:33,847
Lepaskan aku, Berengsek!

239
00:21:33,930 --> 00:21:35,682
Apa yang kau lakukan?
Lepaskan aku!

240
00:21:35,765 --> 00:21:37,141
-Lepaskan aku!
-Jangan bergerak!

241
00:21:41,729 --> 00:21:44,649
Apa kau sudah gila, Gyeong-hui?
