629
00:50:42,929 --> 00:50:44,848
lebih penting.

630
00:50:47,725 --> 00:50:49,477
Apa? Kehidupan politik?

631
00:50:49,978 --> 00:50:51,437
Abadi?

632
00:50:52,814 --> 00:50:55,108
